            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>网购牙齿矫正器靠谱吗？】整牙效果堪比整容？越来越多友友开始注重牙齿美观，牙齿矫正成为一股新潮流。一些网店看准商机，直接向人们销售牙齿矫正器及相关定制服务，号称在家就能完成矫正。那么网购的牙齿矫正器靠谱吗？是“智商税”吗？医院正畸都要被“自助式”矫正所取代了？👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E6%95%B4%E7%89%99%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%A0%AA%E6%AF%94%E6%95%B4%E5%AE%B9%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E6%95%B4%E7%89%99%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%A0%AA%E6%AF%94%E6%95%B4%E5%AE%B9%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#你同意整牙效果堪比整容吗#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （出品：科普中国） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4927032380031013" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">科普中国的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/005ztyuLly1hg7yywcylpj61hc0u01kx02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/2qq7Qh2Wlx087g21LqfC01041201MEDy0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690218962&amp;ssig=IGeAIscnqs&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/CWaoyjOUlx087g22Z2xG01041200VJEs0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1690218962&amp;ssig=UfvEA1OjEb&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/LMdjww8zlx087g21747C01041200CfV