            <description><![CDATA[【今日，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%A7%E6%9A%91%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#大暑#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[太阳]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/w_taiyang-2b1d91ddac.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】①7月23日9时50分迎来大暑，是<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E1%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E6%B0%94%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E1%E4%B8%AA%E8%8A%82%E6%B0%94%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#夏天最后1个节气#</span></a>；②一年中“上蒸下煮”“湿热交蒸”到达极点的时节到了；③温高而气湿，赏荷正当时；④适当减少户外活动，注意室内降温，加强情绪调节。（人民日报） <img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hg6p3fo8r2j20np0zkqbq.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hg6p3g71c6j20np0zktjl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hg6p3gxsicj20np0zkgvl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
